description: This is our traditional workout where you'll get the opportunity to practice calisthenics skills, improve your general strength/fitness, and get to know people!

Come join the DragonFire Family Mon/Wed/Fri at 2:00 PM for a mixed calisthenics and weightlifting workout. Monday's and Friday's will focus on calisthenics and Wednesday's will be specifically weightlifting at the outdoor gym next to the bar park.
